sequenceDiagram
  participant C1 as Client A
  participant C2 as Client B
  participant GW as NGINX /socket.io
  participant CS as chat-service Socket.IO
  participant DB as Message table

  C1->>GW: WebSocket upgrade /socket.io
  GW->>CS: proxied upgrade
  CS-->>C1: socket connected

  C2->>GW: WebSocket upgrade /socket.io
  GW->>CS: proxied upgrade
  CS-->>C2: socket connected

  C1->>CS: emit chat:message(groupId,content)
  CS->>DB: persist message
  CS-->>C1: ack message accepted
  CS-->>C2: broadcast chat:message(newMessage)
